            "body": "Can you give some code that reproduces the crash?\r\n\r\n`__Pyx_PyType_Ready` does set `Py_TPFLAGS_HEAPTYPE`, but it also unsets it afterwards so I don't think that should be an issue. For example we call `PyType_Modified` ourselves on statically allocated types.",
